HEADWORD: nuclear fusion reaction
<hw>nuclear fusion reaction</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A nuclear reaction
in which nuclei combine to form more massive nuclei with the
simultaneous release of energy.</def> <syn><b>Syn. --</b> fusion,
nuclear fusion.</syn>⟦br⟧
